@startuml

title RAG Query - Sequence Diagram

autonumber

participant "Agent Runtime" as Runtime
participant "Knowledge Service" as Knowledge
participant "Policy Engine" as Policy
participant "OpenSearch" as OpenSearch
participant "Foundation Model" as Model
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Audit Service" as Audit

Runtime -> Knowledge: POST /knowledge-bases/{id}/search
Knowledge -> Policy: Validate access and filters
Policy --> Knowledge: Access granted
Knowledge -> Model: Generate query embedding
Model --> Knowledge: Embedding vector
Knowledge -> OpenSearch: Vector + metadata search
OpenSearch --> Knowledge: Ranked chunks
Knowledge -> Knowledge: Apply reranking and citation formatting
Knowledge -> Kafka: Publish knowledge.retrieved
Knowledge --> Runtime: Chunks, scores and citations
Kafka -> Audit: Consume knowledge.retrieved

@enduml
